### Маппинг tools → платформа

| Self-editing tool | Тип памяти | Операция |
|------------------|-----------|----------|
| `core_memory_read` | Working | GET session `__persistent__`, key `__core__` |
| `core_memory_update` | Working | PUT session `__persistent__`, key `__core__` (merge section) |
| `core_memory_replace` | Working | PUT session `__persistent__`, key `__core__` (string replace) |
| `recall_memory_search` | Episodic | POST query |
| `recall_memory_insert` | Episodic | POST ingest |
| `archival_memory_search` | Wiki или RAG | POST query |
| `archival_memory_insert` | Wiki или RAG | POST ingest (async, concept extraction) |
| `archival_memory_update` | Wiki | PATCH concept |
| `archival_memory_delete` | Wiki или RAG | DELETE data |

### Реализация в Agent

Self-editing активируется на уровне Agent:

```json
{
  "name": "Personal Assistant",
  "config": {
    "self_editing": true,
    "core_memory_sections": ["user_profile", "preferences", "current_context", "important_facts"],
    "core_memory_max_tokens": 4000
  },
  "layers": [
    { "memory_type": "working", "role": "core_memory", "priority": 1 },
    { "memory_type": "episodic", "role": "recall_memory", "priority": 2 },
    { "memory_type": "wiki", "role": "archival_memory", "priority": 3 }
  ]
}
```

Когда `self_editing: true`:
- MCP endpoint отдаёт расширенный набор tools (core/recall/archival)
- SDK предоставляет helper для формирования system prompt с core memory injection
- Все self-edit операции логируются в action_log с `actor: "self_edit"`

