## Core Memory Injection

При каждом вызове агента core memory должна быть в system prompt.
SDK предоставляет helper:

```python
from memoryservice import MemoryClient

client = MemoryClient(api_key="ms_live_xxx")
agent = client.agents.get("agent_abc")

# Получить core memory для инъекции в system prompt
core = agent.get_core_memory(user_id="user_123")

system_prompt = f"""You are a personal assistant.

<core_memory>
{core.to_xml()}
</core_memory>

You have access to memory tools. Use them to:
- Update core memory when you learn important things about the user
- Search recall memory for past conversation context
- Store important facts in archival memory
- Keep core memory concise and current — remove outdated info
"""

# Core memory в XML формате:
# <core_memory>
#   <user_profile>Алексей, 34 года, маркетолог</user_profile>
#   <preferences>Краткие ответы. Аллергия на орехи.</preferences>
#   <current_context>Обсуждаем контент-стратегию Q3</current_context>
#   <important_facts>Бюджет 2M руб. KPI 500 лидов.</important_facts>
# </core_memory>
```

